    <abstract>
      <t>   The DetNet data fields defined in Deterministic Latency Action (DLA)
   can be used in enhanced Deterministic Networking (DetNet) to provide
   QoS treatment to achieve deterministic latency.

   This document defines how DetNet data fields are encapsulated in IPv6
   option.

